I'm never present anywhere.

41:08.591 --> 41:11.761
<i>♪ You saw the whole</i>
<i>of the moon ♪</i>

41:11.844 --> 41:15.348
‐[video stops]
‐I think I'm just always so...

41:15.431 --> 41:18.017
