gonna go wrong,

41:18.101 --> 41:19.018
and how am I gonna fix it,

41:19.102 --> 41:19.686
and what's the story
gonna be,

41:19.769 --> 41:21.396
and how am I gonna tell it,

41:21.479 --> 41:22.772
and who am I gonna
tell it to?

41:22.855 --> 41:23.898
I thought that was my problem.

41:23.982 --> 41:27.318
I know.

41:27.402 --> 41:28.736
But that's not really true,
is it?

41:31.072 --> 41:32.615
I mean, look at you,
you've made

41:32.699 --> 41:35.576
one decision after another.

41:35.660 --> 41:36.619
I haven't made any decisions.
I never make any decisions.

41:36.703 --> 41:39.497
I just let shit happen
to me, and then I just

41:39.580 --> 41:41.541
feel bad about it, sad about it.

41:41.624 --> 41:43.126
I just complain about it.

41:43.209 --> 41:45.044
I don't think that's
necessarily true, but okay.

41:45.128 --> 41:47.046
I didn't even plan this wedding;
you did.

41:47.130 --> 41:49.382
‐Well, you were busy.
‐Yeah.

41:49.465 --> 41:50.550
And don't think I don't know
what people would say

41:50.633 --> 41:53.970
if they knew that
I showed up here right now.

41:54.053 --> 41:55.888
"There's Helen,
codependent again."

41:55.972 --> 41:58.141
What people
are we talking about?

41:58.224 --> 42:00.226
