to be with you. You know?

42:04.605 --> 42:05.481
Okay.

42:05.565 --> 42:09.277
And I'm also really
fucking tired

42:09.360 --> 42:10.903
of everyone telling
everyone else

42:10.987 --> 42:12.238
what's good for them.

42:12.321 --> 42:14.782
You know? Nobody does
what's good for them.

42:14.866 --> 42:18.578
And if they do, they
certainly don't enjoy it.

42:20.621 --> 42:22.081
And another thing.

42:22.165 --> 42:23.624
