that stays married

42:23.708 --> 42:25.293
for, let's say, 50 years.

42:25.376 --> 42:27.211
You don't think that
there's an element

42:27.295 --> 42:29.255
of codependency in
that relationship?

42:29.338 --> 42:31.466
I mean, you think these
people would stay married

42:31.549 --> 42:34.594
for half a century
because they wanted to?

42:34.677 --> 42:35.595
That's insane.

42:35.678 --> 42:38.765
Helen, are you okay?
D‐Do you want to...?

42:38.848 --> 42:40.099
Do you want to sit down?

42:40.183 --> 42:42.518
No, I think I might be having a
nervous breakdown, so I just...

42:42.602 --> 42:43.936
it's better if I stand up.

42:44.020 --> 42:44.937
Okay, well, at least

42:45.021 --> 42:47.815
‐have some more salt.
‐That's a good idea.

42:50.276 --> 42:51.652
[grunts]

43:08.336 --> 43:09.337
Do you know, if you had
had an affair 50 years ago,

43:09.420 --> 43:12.006
we never would've broken up?

43:13.883 --> 43:15.968
We never would have mentioned
it, really, to anybody.

43:16.052 --> 43:16.719
You certainly wouldn't have

43:16.803 --> 43:20.014
written a fucking book about it.

43:22.183 --> 43:24.227
And if we had mentioned it,

43:24.310 --> 43:27.814
I would have been given credit
for standing by you.

43:27.897 --> 43:32.235
You know, for putting our family
before my own personal feelings.

43:32.318 --> 43:35.822
I would have been congratulated
for my character.

43:35.905 --> 43:39.700
50 years ago, I would have been
a good fucking wife,

43:39.784 --> 43:40.451
and now I'm the problem.

43:40.535 --> 43:42.662
Well, more like 60 years ago,

43:42.745 --> 43:44.163
‐but I see your point.
‐I mean, I just...

43:44.247 --> 43:45.331
I don't even know
what's going on here.

43:45.414 --> 43:46.374
I don't know what
I'm trying to prove.

43:46.457 --> 43:49.127
I mean, if we both die
and you never find out

43:49.210 --> 43:52.630
that I still love you, what,
do I win a prize or something?

44:03.307 --> 44:04.976
Sorry, what?

44:09.939 --> 44:13.067
I don't know, I think
maybe I am crazy.

44:19.323 --> 44:21.284
Well, you know that's not true.

44:21.367 --> 44:23.202
[sighs]

44:28.791 --> 44:30.668
Look, you know how
I feel about you.

44:30.751 --> 44:32.962
I don't know what
you want me to say.

44:33.045 --> 44:35.131
Um, yes, I do think it's strange

44:35.214 --> 44:37.842
