for a reason and that...

46:12.395 --> 46:14.981
I'm stronger now
because of what happened,

46:15.064 --> 46:18.359
and so I'm better now

46:18.442 --> 46:19.568
than I was
when we were together.

46:19.652 --> 46:23.489
And most of the time, I do
really believe that that's true.

46:25.783 --> 46:29.787
But some days
when I'm feeling really...

46:31.622 --> 46:34.041
...sad or really happy...

46:36.752 --> 46:40.715
And I just think about how
we're not here for long at all.

46:40.798 --> 46:43.050
And when we're gone,
we're gone forever.

46:48.431 --> 46:51.267
Those are the days
I just forget to remember

46:51.350 --> 46:53.311
that it all happened
for the best.

47:09.994 --> 47:12.663
Will you dance with me?

47:17.251 --> 47:19.128
On our daughter's wedding day?

47:35.269 --> 47:36.479
